STRATEGY MEMO — NovaTech Latin America Market Entry
===================================================

Market Sizing (2025)
- TAM (LatAm SCM SaaS): $1,836.0MM
  Calculation: $85.0B IT spend × 18% B2B SaaS × 12% SCM
- SAM (mid-market, 100-2,000 employees): $826.2MM
